Dialogs.Dialog: ▲主人公＊▲. It's raining. But it may be nice to have a different atmosphere than usual.
That's right, maybe not that bad.
▲主人公＊▲. Isn't it romantic to date on a snowy day?
▲主人公＊▲. Fufu,boys also have big umbrellas.
Yes, I came a little earlier. It's snowing, so we can have fun.
Sorry to make you wait. It's raining.
Yes. I hope it stops raining...
Sorry, I was a little late.
It's fine. I was watching the snow. See, it's beatiful.
It's wet, so be careful. Don't hurt yourself, okay?
Sorry. I made you wait while it was snowing...
Geez, I've been waiting for a long time... Why were you so late?
I'm glad you're here. I came to pick you up because it's late... what happened?
I couldn't wait, so I came. Is that okay?
（Did you arrive a little early? Would you like to hang around...）
（I'm sorry, I was at the convenience store and it took me more time than expected）
Sorry! I arrived early, but I took a detour to pass the time....
（Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. It look like she hasn't noticed yet）
It's hurt's... It was a bad move...
（Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲, she hasn't... I should call her）
Hello? Huh? I called you right now?
I also called you... It seems we did it at the same time.
Sorry to make you wait. I'm glad I found you.
I don't like that face, it's disturbing. See you!
（Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you talking to someone?）
Ah, there you are... Well, that's why I came with you!
Sorry, I kept you waiting. Were you being picked up?
Was it that?... I'm really bad with that kind of people. Don't keep me waiting next time, okay?
There you are. I'm sorry, I'm late.
Wha-, I'm sorry! I made a mistake!
I'm sorry, you're similar from the back...
That's why....Geez, I don't know anymore.
No, it's fine I was late too. I just arrived...
It's rare. I thought I had to apologize.
Me too. But I'm glad I didn't make you wait.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, didn't you come? Where are you?）
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Were you trying to do something?
I wanted to cover your eyes and ask "Who is it!". I almost got it.
It's terrible, I'll be so late... Anyway, I have to change my clothes!
I came to pick you up. Did you forget our promise?
I'm sorry, I was doing something and I didn't realize...
You were in a hurry... You know, your clothes are inside out.
Wow! I'm sorry, I'll change now!
（...Huh? I wonder what are you doing,▲高嶺＊＊▲）
Hey,▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing crouched like that?
Yes, it was cute♪ He ran away because you shouted.
（Emm ...Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is talking with some foreigners）
He was asking for directions ... He's from Germany.
No, in English. Chatting in German is a bit...
（She's not here...? It's rare for▲高嶺＊＊▲ to be late）
I'm sorry to keep you waiting.
Mama took my umbrella... I chased after her, and when I noticed I was late.
Huh? I something wrong with me?
Your hair is boucing. Bed hair? or, is it because of the humidity?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What's wrong? Is anything troubling you?
You butt? No, I don't there's anything bad.
I'm glad... I stumbled over with snow... Oh, I'm okay because I'm not hurt.
（Falling with the snow. ▲高嶺＊＊▲... I'm sorry, but I wanted to see it）
▲主人公＊▲. Look, look, I made this while I was waiting.
Wow, a snow Daruma... It's a work of art.
I did my best♪ Let's take a picture.
（I don't think I was late... It's better to keep silent）
The wind is blowing your hair... It's a bit messed up, right? Here, crouch a little.
（It's embarrassing... But, if▲高嶺＊＊▲ fixes it, I'm lucky）
What happened? ...Is it hard to say?
Good. I didn't think you would care so much...
I tried wearing the gift you gave me. Does it look good?
Did you notice I was wearing this? I like it.
I tried wearing your gift... What do you think?
I'm glad. If you're happy, I want to wear it all the time... I'm kidding.
I'm glad. I'll continue to cherish it.
I don't care... It's something you gave me...
Should I change it?...Well, I'll think about it.
Then, don't you like this? So....
Is that so? It's okay, but tell what you think, okay?
You say something? ...It's okay, tell me.
Emm... but I just changed it. Hmm....
That is... How should I take that?
My hair is growing, right? It's time to cut it.
Maybe I was expecting you to say so.
That's right... I should do it.
My new hairstyle... How do you like it?
I changed my hair color. Did you notice it?
Yay♪ ...I'm kidding, I'm glad I changed it.
Emm.... is this no good?... I was a little confident...
If I get that kind of reaction, I'll be in trouble...
Hey, what did you make for lunch?
What will you do for dinner?
I'm getting hungry at this hour....
Yes! I'm already hungry... I'm kidding.
Will we eat there? Yes, it's okay.
I wonder if it's good now...
Ah, it looks like it's sunny...
Clouds are coming, right? Will it rain?
Ah, snow! Hey~, how long will it rain?
It looks like it's raining outside, right?
It might be better to hurry.
It's bad, it's coming down. What should we do...
Would you like to go there?
Yes, I like that. Shall we go?
Geez... Don't ask me things like that.
I want you to be a little more patient....
No, you can still hold the umbrella... Right?
It rain, and you'll get wet... Right?
No. You don't have to bother doing this, right?
No... I don't want to do that.
It's difficult to walk because we can lose balance....
Want to take a pic here? It's okay... Isn't it funny?
Photo? Since it's a big deal, take a cute one... I'm kidding.
Stop it... Maybe I can't laugh right now.
It's still early, but I'm hungry. Would you like to eat something together?
I'm hungry, do you want to go for lunch?
It's dinner time. What will you do?
I'm actually hungry... shall we go?
I... I think it's good now.
And I even make sure to bring my umbrella... it's a pity.
Ah, I brought my umbrella. I messed my chance of sharing an umbrella, I'm kidding.
Did you forget your umbrella? Then... scooch inside.
If you don't have and umbrella, please...
Did you bring an umbrella? Well then... come to Aika's umbrella▼
Do you have an umbrella? Well then, let's use this together.
Do you have an umbrella? Then, let's use this umbrella!
I'm glad I forgot it... I'm kidding.
Did you forget your umbrella? Then, let's use this one together.
Thank you. I didn't forget it on purpose, okay?
It's raining, and I didn't bring an umbrella...
Sorry, don't you feel like doing that?
Hey~... Are you not watching now??
Emm~... That is the reason why.
I prefer this one. Is that no good?
... It's not enough with just your hands.
... I'm sorry, I think I made a mistake.
So that was it... Hey~, since we're here, why don't we have a date here?
（If ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is fine with it, then it's okay...）
Huh... Hey~, is it right here?
... I wonder if I made a mistake.
I see... We're running out of time, should we do it here?
（If ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is okay with it, then it's fine...）
Hey~ hey~, what are we playing?
I'm going to change it. Which one do you want to play?
Can I do it once more! It's okay?
... I want to play some more.
Alright, I'll live up to your expectations!
Good work. What do we do next?
When things don't go well, no matter what you do...
I woke up early today and made lunch. Shall we eat here?
Um, I've prepared a lunch box. Want to eat?
Today's lunch is a beloved wife lunch♪ I'm kidding.
Want to come to my house?
... Shall we go home after all?
Ah, is that so... I understand.
Your home?... Yes. I want to see it.
... There, there. Do you want to play? I'm sorry, I'm on a date right now.
It was a doggy. Thank you for worrying about me.
I see, it just wanted to play.
Ah, that kid... it's small and alone. Is he lost?
It's nice his mom was nearby. It was thanks to ▲高嶺＊＊▲ for realizing immediately!
It just happens. You were the one who found her.
Huh, my phone... Hey~, can you call me?
Ah~... I'm sorry, I just put it in a different place.
Yes, I'm sorry. It was Papa, he didn't seem to have any particular reason...
It's dangerous, even though it's the pedestrian side road.
Yes. But I'm okay, because you protect me.
You there, what are you doing?
It's a survey of some kind?
I'm a little bad that at that. If you come, you'll want to run away.
Do you have to read it?
I can read the mail later. You're more important.
I see... I'm a little shy.
Am I always your top priority? ...I'm kidding.
She looked like Sharapova, famous female tennist... she's gone. I'm a fan!
Excuse me. Can you take us a photo?
Yes, it's fine... Please, wait a second.
They were a nice couple. But... we're not losing to them, right?
Hmm? Oh, what's wrong with you two..
... Ah, it's you guys. See you, be careful.
Geez, why are you so nervous?
Is it time for lunch yet?
It's dinner time... Shall we eat?
I made lunch, thinking you would come.
Is it okay if we extend our date?
What are your plans after this? I would be happy to be with you more.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ are you good on time? I want to continue our date...
Yes. I want to be more together.
I'm glad, then let's go somewhere else.
Time... Maybe just a little longer.
Okay. Then I have to hurry and decide where to go.
I want to... But, I have plans after this.
If that's the case, we can't help it. See you next time...
I'm glad you invited me, but it's time...
Is that so... Then it's okay.
Geez, I don't have time anymore.
I'll invite you to my home.
Um. Can I borrow your shoulder?
A little... I want to lean on you... can I?
Can I stick next to you?
I'm happy... I don't mind staying like this forever.
Being next to you... I like it the most.
We arrived early? It would be okay if it was always like this.
Haha, I'm in trouble... For the time being, let's get off.
Ah... You saw my sleeping face.... Geez, forget it please?
Can you lend me a shoulder?
I feel you right next to me...
You body is a little warm.
Hey~, what if I can't stop being like this?
Um, don't you want to be together some more? We can go to my room.
Yes. I want to be with you too.
The time is short... I'm worried.
I want to be with you a little more... Can I go to your room?
Really? I'll be your guest, okay?
Is that so... I suppose it's a bother if you say it suddenly.
Sorry. I didn't get ready to get people in.
Ah, so there was a gift.
Aika! If you're back, enter quickly.
Hey~, since we're here, why don't we go home?
If you like, why don't we go home? Papa and Mama are not there, so I can't entertain you.
Is that so... See you next time.
Thank you for today. Take care in your way back.
Be careful on your way back. See you...
While we were in a fight... How were you?
It was a pain not being able to speak with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Me too. I'm so happy today... I wish this makes us closer.
Yes, that's it. From now, let's get along better.
You know... I was really angry last time, okay?
Yes. If you're angry, then we can't have a date.
Same to you, thank you for making up with me.
Thank you for today. It's a good thing we were able to make up..
That's right. We couldn't date like this if we were fighting.
Yes, of course. I don't want to fight anymore.
